These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
City: berlin, liverpool, hannover
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| City   | hannover | liverpool | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, trance, folk
1. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | folk | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, japanese
1. the canadian is in an even position##4
2. the canadian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
3. the japanese is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Nationality   | argentine | canadian | japanese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, balloon-flower, begonia
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Flower   | orchid | begonia | balloon-flower |

